\id HEB
\ide  UTF-8
\h Waebrania 
\toc1 Waebrania 
\toc2 Waebrania 
\toc3 heb 
\mt1 Waebrania  
\c 1
\cl Sura ya 1 
\p
\v 1 Eimisiekhe eigilutile uNguluve alikhunchova navankukhu veito ukhugendelenya muvanya malago.  
\v 2 Eimi seikhi mingi na seikhi mingi na khunjila inchili papingi. Puleino mufigono ifi ifyutulinafyo, uNguluve anchoviele nufwe muswambe, uvi ambeikhile ukhuva mwenevuhale va finu fyooni, uviyuywa mu mwene apelile ikhilunga.  
\v 3 Umwana va mwene vielumuli lwa vudwadwa wa mwene, ulugeendo lwa yumwene mwene ulwa vutenguleilo wa mwene, nuvieipikhu fyolelencha ifinu fyooni ni limenyu lya makha ga mwene. Vuamalile uluvalancho lwavutula nongwa wa mbivi atamile pasi khukhivokho eikyandyo eikyavuvaha khukyanya ukhwa.  
\v 4 Aviele inonu ukhulutilila avasuhwa, yiehwanine ndielitawa eilyahalile avasuhwa yiehwanine ndielitawa eilyahalile umulivelile linonu ukhuhutila eilitawa lyavo.  
\v 5 Ulwakhuva puvisuhwa mukhi avyagelile ukhunchova, “Uve uliemanango, eilelo nivile dadaayo?” Avuye, “Niva daada khumweene, navope iva mwana khulyune?”  
\v 6 Avuye, usiekhe ugu uNguluve andeetile ung'oliwa utanchi uvakhilunga, aiita, “Avasuhwa vooni va Nguluve pulusutu viesayage khumwene.”  
\v 7 Ukhukongana navasuhwa iita, “Umwene uviaipela avasuhwa va mwene wehuva mepo, navavombi va mwene ukhuva ndimincha mwoto.”  
\v 8 Puleino ukhukongana nu mwana lita, “Eikhigoda kyako eikya lwangula, Nguluve, kyasikhu nchooni ni sikhu chooni. Ulubikhi lwa vunkuludeeva vwakho pu lubikhi lwa yeilweli.  
\v 9 Unogilwe eilweli nukhu kalala uvudenyaji wa ndagielo, puleino uNguluve, Nguluve vakho, akhubakhile imono ncha luhekhelo lekhulutilida avanino.”  
\v 10 Apo pavulengulielo, Vitwa waveikhile ulyulo lwa khilunga. Ikyanya mbombo ncha mavookho gakho.  
\v 11 Yanchiyaganikha, puuve vupivenchage epyo. Nchooni nchi nangikha ndumwenda.  
\v 12 Puyavukhunchifugiyi liehania ndeilikoti nchoope yanchiha mbukha ndumwenda gwakhufwala. Puuve veve yulayula, na gimiakha gyakho sagiladuga.”  
\v 13 Puleino kwa suhwa aleikhu uNguluvi anchoovile useikhe gugyooni, “Tama eikhivokho kyango eikya khundyo impakha nipya nikhuvapela avatavangwa vaakho ukhuva khigoda kya malunde gakho”?  
\v 14 Pu, avasuhwa vooni samepo einchunchisuhi we ukhuvatanga nukhuvalolela vala uvuya khiva vihala uvupokhi?   
\c 2
\cl Sura ya 2 
\p
\v 1 Puleino lusutu tuviekhe mbulongolo ukhulutilila khugala ugutuga pulikhe, ukhuta putulekhe ukhulengiwa khutale nago  
\v 2 Ulwakhuva yiegave uvujumbwe uvuvaunchoviwe na vasuhwa vwa yielweli, pukhila vunangi nuvugalukhi vukyupilila uluvungu iwene.  
\v 3 Putukavaga ndakhiikhi ukhwipokha uvupokhi uvuvaha noluvu? — uvupokhi vuwa pavutanchi wa nchoviwe Nutwa nukhuvonekha khulyufwe nakhuvala uvuvapulikhe.  
\v 4 U Nguluve voope avuvonisye khufihwani, nifidego, na mumbombo imbaha inchilipapingi, nakhuvuvonole wa mepo umbalanche inchuanchigavile ukhu kongana nuvunogwe wa mwene yuywa.  
\v 5 U Nguluve sakhiviekhe eikhilunga ikhikoncha, eikhyutukhukhinchovelela inongwa ncha kyeene, pasi pa vasuhwa.  
\v 6 Puleino umunu nongi atuvuliele aponu nongi vuita, “Umunu vie veeni, pu ave vakhu kumbukha? Pamo mwana va munu, nekhe undolelee?  
\v 7 Upelile umunu ukhuva ideebe ukhulutilila avasuhwa; ufwulinche uluding'olielo lwa wudwaadwa nu lwimikho. (Nchingahincha: amamenyu aga. “Umbikhile pakyanya pa mbombo nchakho, gasimuli mbusimbe uwukhatale.)  
\v 8 Uviekhile khila khinu pasi pamalunde gakho.” puleino uNguluve aveikhile khila khinu pasi pa munu. Sakhile khile khinu kyukyooni khikyo khisikhuli pasi pa mwene. Puleino ulu lieno satwilola tukhaale khila khinu khingave pasi pamwene.  
\v 9 Paninie niyo, twilola umwene uviapeliwe mukhasekhe pasi ukhulutiliela avasuhwa— uYesu, uvi, savule yavunkuvilwa wamwene nuvufwe wa mwene, afwalei nchiwe uludinglulielo lwa wudwadwanu khwi mikhiwa. Pu leino nduhungu lwa Nguluve uYesu avonji nche uvufwe wa mwene, savuli ya munu uvie avenchaga.  
\v 10 Lwale lunoomu ukhuta uNguluve, ulwakhuva khila khinu pukhile savuli ya mwene nukhugendela mumweene, aanogile ukhwincha na vaana vavingi mbudwaaada nukhuva anogile ukhupela eindongonchi mumbupokhi vwavo vadulufu mumbo nkuvilwa wa mwene.  
\v 11 Ulwakhuva vuvavieli ula uviveikha ulwimikho navala uvuviveikhiwa ulwimikho, vooni vihuma mukhivumbukhu khimo, uNguluve ulwakhuv khu eili ula uvikhuvaveikha ulwimikho khwa Nguluve sifwa isoni ukhuta valukolwe.  
\v 12 Iita, “Yanikhuvavula eilitaw lyakho khuva lukololwango, yanikhwimba ukhuta uve ukhuhuma igati mundulundamano.”  
\v 13 Hange iita, “Yanikhwide ekha mumwene.'” Na khange, “'Lola apa punile na vaana uvu uNguluve amele.”  
\v 14 Pulieno ulwakhuva avaana va Nguluve vooni vikyupilila umbili nu kisa, vuvuwa na yu Yesu aupilile ifinu filafila, ukhuta ukhugendela mbufwe akave ukhufweeyula ula uvyalienuvu vaha wa vufwe, uvi uyu vindugu.  
\v 15 Eiyi yale ewo ukhuta avaveikhe mbulegeefu vala vooni uvu ukhugenela mbudwanchi wavufwe vataamage imilamile gyavo gyooni mutwa.  
\v 16 Mbwayielweli savasuhwa uvuikhuvatanga. Puleino ikhuvalanga avanki vumbukhu khya Abrahamu.  
\v 17 Puleino yale lusutu umweene ave ndavalukololwe vamwene munjila nchooni, Ukhuta pu ave intekhenchi umbaha unyakhisa hange igoloofu khuvaanu va Nguluve, nu khuta ave na makha gakhuhumya ulusyiekhilo lwa mbivi ncha vaanu.  
\v 18 Ulwakhuva uYiesu yuywa nkuvilwe nukhugeliwa alienamakha gakhuvalanga vala avaviseliwa.   
\c 3
\cl Sura ya 3 
\p
\v 1 Ulwa khuva, valukololwango mwievalanche, mwimuhangile nu lwilango ulwakhukyanya, mnsagielage uYesu, unsukhwa nu Untwa Umbaha uvitukhumwidika.  
\v 2 Alee mwiediheinchi kwa Nguluve uvambikhile, nduvu uvu Mose ale mwiedihienchi munyumba yoni iya Nguluve.  
\v 3 Ulwakuva uYesu avakhiwe ukhuva idwanchiwa imbaha ukhulutela kwa Mose, ulwakuva uvanchengile inyumba viivaliwa ukhuva ualisima ilivaha ukulutila inyumba eiyene.  
\v 4 Ulwakuva khila nyumba yinchengiwa nu munu unoongi, ukhuva uvinchenga khila khinu vei Nguluve.  
\v 5 Lweli u Mose aale mwiedihinchi ndu mbombi munyumba yoni iya Nguluve, ukunkonaana ni mbombo inchu nchilachoviwa unsieke ugukhwincha.  
\v 6 Ulwakhuva uKlisite vee mwana mumbuloleli wa nyumba ya Nguluve. Nayufwe tulinyumba yamwene eingave tukhwibatielila imbeive ukhweka ngancha, nulwimeikho ulwakhwevona.  
\v 7 Ulwakuva, nduvu Mepe mbalanche uvuinchova, “Ilelo, iengave tupulika alimenyu ilyamwene,  
\v 8 Pwulekhage ukhuyivike inumbula yakho ukhuva ng'afu nduvu AvaIsilaheli nduvuvavombile muvugalukhe khukungela, unsiekhe ugwakhugeliwe mundudasi.  
\v 9 Uugu ngwu gwale insiekhe ugwu udada veitu vakhangela nunsiekhe, ugwamiaka arobaini, vakanchivona imbombo nchango.  
\v 10 Pwunavipile nuvukholwa uwa. Nikhanchova, 'Viyaga khila nseikhe munumbu nchavene, na savanchimanyile injila nchango.  
\v 11 Nduvuniekhi ejyeigile mundyoyo lyango: Savakhinglele munduhekhelo lwango.”  
\v 12 Muvinchage miho, valukholo, ulwakuva uyugwiva pwugule unteima unangi ugusagu kwedika khuvalyumo veinyu, inumbula yiyo yiluta khuvutali nu Nguluve uvei mwumi.  
\v 13 Pwu muvunganage khilasiku khilamunu nu nine, ulwakuvu khila khigono munogwage, ukuva uyunge mundyumwe aleke ukuva ninumbu imbivi.  
\v 14 Ulwakuva tuhanga nu Klisite nukwibatana na masage na makha mumwene ukhuhuma kuvutengulilo ukufika kuvumalilo.  
\v 15 Ulwakuva eili lisilile ukhunchoviwa, “Ilelo mungapulike ilimenyu lya mwene, mulekhage ukhunchivika inumbu nchenyu ukhuva ngumu, nduvu Avaislaeli vavombile unsiekhe uguvagalwikhe.  
\v 16 Vuvaveni avo avampulike uNguluve nu kugaluka? Savakale vuvala voni uvu Mose avalongwinche ukhuhuma ku Misili?  
\v 17 Vuvaveni uvu uNguluve avavipile kumyaka alobaini? Ndavuvaninie vala avavombile imbivi, uvuimivieli gyavene gyafwile ndukungu?  
\v 18 Vuvaveni uvuuNguluve aejyeegile ukhuta suvalingiela munduhekelo lwa mwene, nda vuvala uvusamwide umwene?  
\v 19 Twilola ukhuta savawesinche ukwingiela munduhekhelo lwamwene ulwakuva savamweidekhe.   
\c 4
\cl Sura ya 4 
\p
\v 1 Ulwakuva, tunogiewa ukhuva miho, ukuva mugaati mulyufwe sapilondiwa umunu yumo avyakhiva ivoneka eilemwa ukhufikha kuludeva ulyakukyanya ulwa Nguluve.  
\v 2 Ulwakuva lweli, tupulike eilimenyu ilya lugatalukho ilya Nguluve ilyuvatuvulile ufwe ndava Islaeli uvuvale nalyo, hange ilimenyu ielyo salyavatange vavo vapulikhe uvusavakhongine nulwidiko ulwa.  
\v 3 Ufwe yufwe, tweedike ulweolieko-ufwe fwe tulimugaati tulingila mundugataluko lula, nduvuinchova, “Nduvunaijyiegile munduvipo lwango, Vusavalingiela mundugataluko lwango.” Anchovile ile, ulwakuva imbombo nchoni inchavombiwe ncha silile ukhuhuma kuvutengulilo uwakhilunga.  
\v 4 Ulwakuva unchovile badebe khusiku iyalekhela khumo, “UNguluve agaatalwike ilijuuva eilya lekhela khumo akhanchileka imbombo nchoni.”  
\v 5 Ulwakhuma munchovile, “Vusavalingiela ndugaataluko ulwamwene.”  
\v 6 Ulwakhuva eiwo, ukhuhuma ndugaataluko ulwa Nguluve pwu kuvale avasigiile ukwingiela, ukhuhuma kuvanya Islaeli avingi uvuvapulike eilimenyu ielinonu ilyalugaataluko lyamwene ilyakwingiela savaingeele ulwakhuva savapulikhagaa,  
\v 7 UNguluve hange aviekhile ilijuuva ilienge elyutwita “Ilelo.” Umwene aviekhile ilijuuva ile ukhugeendela khwa Ndaveti, uvianchovile kunsiekhe untali khugala agaanchoviwe kuvutengulilo, '“Ilelo mungapulikage ilimenyu lya mwene, mlekhe ukhunchivieka inumbu nchenyo ukhuva ng'afu.”  
\v 8 Ingave uYoshua avapile ulugataluko, uNguluve pwusakhale inchova kulijuuva ilienge khavili.  
\v 9 Ulwakhuva yiesigile isabato iyalugaataluko khuvanu ava Nguluve.  
\v 10 Ulwakuva uveingile mundugaatalukho ulwa Nguluve vie mwene agaatalwikhe ukhukongana ni mbombo inchamwene, nduvu uNguluve avombile khumwene.  
\v 11 Pwutuvinchage nukhunogwa ukwingiela mundugaataluko lula.  
\v 12 Ulwakuva ilimenyu lya Nguluve lyumi hange lilina makha mundu yitema khunu na khunu. Khange linyanya ukhuluteilila ukhuwesa ukhugaava inumbula inchamepo, ni mono inchili mugaati mufilungielo fya mwene.  
\v 13 Iliwesya ukhuvomba amasaage ga wiegaane wa numbula ya mwene. Khisikuli ikhivumbikhe ikyefihili khumiho gaa Nguluve. Ulwakhuva khila khinu khilipavuvalafu khivonekha khumiho khumunu uvalala ivonesya imbaleelo.  
\v 14 Pavulongolo tulava nu untekhenchi umbaha uvingile khukyanya, uYesu umwana va Nguluve, khumakha twibatelile ulweidiko lwetu.  
\v 15 Ulwakuva asikuli untekhenchi umbaha uvisiwesya ukwitwika iekhisa nu uvudekhedekhe weitu, ulwakhuva umwene vyalikhugeilwa khunjila nchoni nduufwe, apange umwene uvyalivuvule imbivi.  
\v 16 Pwu twinchage namakha pakhinyalwangula ikyantwa ikyaluhungu, pwutwupilile ikhisa nukwupilila uluhungu ulwakhututanga unsiekhe wuu tulemilwe.   
\c 5
\cl Sura ya 6 
\p
\v 1 Ulakuva untekechi umbavaha uvyahalilwe ukhuhuma na mbanu, uhalilwe ukwima kuvanu mufinu ifya Nguluve ukuta ahumie enekelo ya mbivi.  
\v 2 Ivwesya ukuvatolela mu mbwololo nu vupelwa nu lukani ulakova vope mwene achunguliwe nu vulemwa.  
\v 3 Ku njila eye, anogile ukuhumia enekelo ku mbivi cha mnene ndu umu avombile ku mbivi cha vanu.  
\v 4 Asikuli umunu uvigega ilisima ele kusavuli ya mwene, umwene impaka ilangiwe nu Nguluve, nduvu zle u Aron.  
\v 5 Ata uKlisite sa iyepe ilisima yuvwya mwene ukuva intekhechi imbaha. Ulakuva uNguluve achovile nu mwene, “Uve ve mwana vango, ilelo nivile Dadayo.”  
\v 6 Ndu uvu achovile puvunge, “Uve veve intekhechi koke whani kya Melkizedeki.”  
\v 7 Munseki ugwa mwene ugwa mbili, adovile nu kudovela, andovile uNguluve na kulwihochi, ku mwene uvi ivnesye ukumpoka ukuhuma kuvufwe. Kuvudekedeke vwa mwene kwa Nguluve, apulikike.  
\v 8 Upu ingave ale mwana, amanyile uwedihichi kumbombo ichontesiche.  
\v 9 Agingachiove na ku njila iye avombike ku kila munu uvi ikumwediko ukuva vupoki vwa siku choni,  
\v 10 Pa kwimikiwa nu Nguluve pakuva untekhechi umbaha ukulutile unseke gwa Melkizedeki.  
\v 11 Tulinagwo mingi agakuchova kunongwa ya Yesu, pu pakafu ukuvavola ukova umwe mule volo ukupulika.  
\v 12 Puingave ku kaseki aka mukanogile ukuva va vamanyisi, mukale ukuta umunu ale avamanyisye ulumanyisyo ulutachi ulwa ndagilo cha limenyu lya Nguluve. Munogile ulukama sio ikwakulya ikikafu.  
\v 13 Pu ulakova uvi inywa ulu kama lwenu, inchila welewa mu mbofu mbwe uasa yelweli ulakuva mukale mulivaana.  
\v 14 Kuluvafu ulunge, ikyakulya ikikafu kwa vanu avakulu, vala uvu vivwesya lekulehania uvuyelweli nu vuvivi vamanyisiwe ukuvumanya uvunonu nu vuvivi.   
\c 6
\cl Sura ya 6 
\p
\v 1 Pu tunakile ukyutumanyile tasi mbufumbwe wa Kilisite, tunogile ukuva nulugimbo ukuluta mbudulufu, tuleke kange ukuvika ulwatu lwa kupelela mu mbombo ichi chi chila womi nu lwidiko mwa Nguluve,  
\v 2 nu lwetu lwa lumanyisyo lwa lwocho, nu kuvavekela amavoko, uvuchoka vwa vafwe, nu vuhigi vwa siku choni.  
\v 3 Pu twagahile ndavule upwu uNguluve atuhovokile.  
\v 4 Ulakova sayi kwidihana kuvala ava vale ndumuli lutachi, uvu vavonjiche ikikungilwa kya kukyanya, nu kuva va lulu ndamano lwa mepo mbalache,  
\v 5 Nu ava vonjiche uvunonu vwa limenyo lya Nguluve na kumaka aga kunseki ugwichi,  
\v 6 Pu vakagwa - sayikwidihana kange ukwidi hana ukuvakilivola kange ukhoma mu toba. Ulakona vikukilivu la kavile umwana va Nguluve mbukuvilwa munumbula cha vene, pu vikumbika ukuta vakubendiwa pavuvalafu.  
\v 7 Ula kuva ung'anga ugwupilile ifula eyiyitima kila senki, yimecha ufinu ifyu avanu avavombile pakyalo, vikwapilile ulusayo lwa Nguluve.  
\v 8 Upu ingave gihupa imitoni ulungupa, ni kidilu, yichila kinu na yesiga lile padebe ukukotoliwa. Kuvumalilo vya pene kukuyezya.  
\v 9 Upu ingava twitande, vagane tukuvidikala kumambo amanunu aga ku lyumwe na aga mbupoku.  
\v 10 Ulakova u Nguluve sa mbivi ukuta itamwa imbombo chenu nu lugano ulumuvonisye munditanuva lya mwene, mu ile mwavavombile mukhuva vombele.  
\v 11 Twinogwa ficho ukuta kila munu avonesye ulugimbo lulalula ukusika kumwisyo kya wayelweli wa vukifu.  
\v 12 Satwinogwa muve volo, pu muve wakongi va vala avihala indaganiye ku njila ya hwidiko nu vwe yumilichi.  
\v 13 Pu uNguluve avile apile u Abrahamu indagavie ampile ku kuvwami wa mwene, ulakuna ale avicho sa idiegile kuyuafe umunu yoyoni uvi umbaha kuliko voni.  
\v 14 Atile, “'Lweli nikukusaya, kange, nikukukweongeleja ikipapo kwako.”  
\v 15 Ku njili iye u Abrahamu au upilile ukyu kyale ndagani vu agulile nu kwiyumilicha.  
\v 16 Ulakova avanu vikidiega kumbaha kulutilila kuvoni na kunuvisyo ku mbombo chomi ku kwidiega kuvugayilweli.  
\v 17 Wakati uNguluve alipoamua kuonesha kwa uwazi zaidi kwa warithi wa ahadi kusudi lake zuri lisilobadilika, alilithibitisha kwa kiapo.  
\v 18 Pu uNguluve avile alamwile lekuvika pavuvalafu ficho kuvahale va ndaganie kuvufumbwe vwa mwene uvusavukwanduka, mu umva uNguluve siwesya ukuchova uvudesi, ufwe yufwe tunyilile kupupoki nu kuginga ehwa inumbula mu maka ga lusuvilo niliviki vivwe mbulongo ndiumwe.  
\v 19 Tulinavwo uvakifu ukuta liwe ilikangafu nu kuhuvile inumbula cheto, uvukifu uvu vukwiufila ingati kusana kumwenda.  
\v 20 UYesu aingile aponu apo ukhuva indongochi vetu, wu avombike ukuva intekhechi imbaha nukuchila kusila lusuku ukuhuma kwa Melkizedeki.   
\c 7
\cl Sura ya 7 
\p
\v 1 Yekhale nde uMelkizezedeki, utawa va Salemu, undogoji vangolove uyavile khokyanya uyavile agine nu Abrahamu ahuwiyile ukhoma khuhubuda avatawa akhasaya.  
\v 2 UAbrahamu akhapile popani ninye khela ya kumi yakhela khenu ekhavile akhetekile. Elitawa lya “Melkizedeki” utavala wa woyelyeli, nutawala va Selemu” ulyahuva utavala va vavogolofu.”  
\v 3 Alivovole ubaba, alevovole umama, alevovole avazazi, alevovole uvotengolelo wasihu wala umwisyo ywasihu nchamwene. Badala ya apoisigala imbaha vasihu nchoni, kama mwana va Ngolove.  
\v 4 Ufihelelelage ukhuta umunu uyuakha vile imbaha itawala. Uzazi veto Uiburahimu akhapile vyoni ivya kumi ifinu ifinonu iufyahatolile khuvita.  
\v 5 Nuwohakika ekhekelo khavalawi khehapohile eofisi ya tavala vahalenayo ni amri uhuhuma hululagelo, ukhulundamanya ekumi uhuhuma huvanu, vavo vihuma uhumana na vaisilaeli avaninye nulundamano ululuhumana na vene ikhekolo khya Abrahamu.  
\v 6 Ulyahova uMelkizedeki, yuyua, ahale vovole ekhekolo kha valawi, akhapokhile yenio ya kumi ukhuhumana nu Abrahamu, akhasaya, uyahavile neuhadi.  
\v 7 Apo sayebeliwe uhuta umunu udebe isayiwa nombaha.  
\v 8 Khulijambo ele umunu uyipo hela yemo eyakumi ifya elinchova leemo, ulyahova hulijambo elenge yomo uyapohile yehavoliwe ndoyo itama.  
\v 9 Ne namna ya khochova, Ulawi uyapohile yemo ya kumi, nuyu ahahombile yemo ya kumi khwa Abrahamu,  
\v 10 Ulyakhuva uLawi akhavite mvi na ifya dadaye vamwene Uibrahimu useheugowagine nuMelkizedeki nu Abrahamu.  
\v 11 Inave uvokamelefu uvahawesehine uhugendela uvutawala wa Lawi, (Poapo avanu vipohela ululagelo), khuhale nulihitaji lihi hutawala uyunge ukhwinoha ufyano gwa Melkizedeki, sio ukhwelangiwa nopangelelo ugwa Haruni?  
\v 12 Ulyahuva uvutawala yavubadeleha, polunugiwa ululagelo lyope lubabadeleha.  
\v 13 Kyuyunu humambo aga akhacho viwe ukhuhusu elikabila elenge, uhukhuma khwemwene hakuna aliye hudumela ekhetehelo.  
\v 14 Isalinchi sahihi uhuta umbaha Veto ahumilee khu Yuda, ilikabila lyelyo uMose sahataje uhusu avatechenchi.  
\v 15 Aga agaginchoviwa khuvuvalafu hata angave itehenchi uyunge ikhomela khofyana gwa Melkizedeki.  
\v 16 Utekhenchi uywa sio aliyomo yoyusa avile itawala khukyonya husingi gwa lulagelo inchihuseha nuvohyolya wa munu, khusingi gwangofu iyamaisha gagosagawesye uhunangeha.  
\v 17 Nuvusimbe vusuhudela ukhohusu umwene, “Uveve teheji sihu nchoni khufumo gwa Melkizedeki.”  
\v 18 Ulyuhova ululagelo ulukhalongwile lukavehiwe pulokanji khuhava salulenkofaa.  
\v 19 Ewo ululagelo salulenkovomba khokhoni akhekamelihe. Ulyohova, pahalepo uwokafu uwononu khuago tuhasogelela uNguluve.  
\v 20 Nuvokafu uvo uvononu savo hahumile bila khonchova ekheapo, khuele avateheji avange savahatole ekheapo khokhyoni.  
\v 21 Ulwahova uNguluve akhato lile ekheapo usekhe ugwa nchovile ukhuhusu uYesu, “Ungolove apile sibadelesya amasage gamwene.' uve vetenchi isihu nchoni.”  
\v 22 Ulyahova unguleve ainchile khusamani ya ululagonu ulunonu.  
\v 23 Uwoye lyeli, ukhufya hubela avatehenchi ukhuvomba isikhu nchoni. Ulyakhova vahalepo avatekhenchi avange, uyumu baada ya vayonge.  
\v 24 Ulyahuva uNguluve itama sihu nchoni uvutekhenchi wamwene savubadeleha.  
\v 25 Umwomwene lwesya nu vogolofu ukhukamelesya uvohela avanhusogelela uNguluve ukhugenda khumwene, ulyakhova itama nuhudova khuvene.  
\v 26 Potehenchi umbaha nduyu inagiwa khulyofe, uyalevovole imbivi, alevowole inongwa, isafi, uyahatengiwe, ukhuma khumbivi, unchile khukyanya khuliko khukinya.  
\v 27 Umwene ahale bila sida, ekhehwani avatekhechi avavaha, ukhuhumya esadakha khela sihu, khumbivi nchasambi nchamwene yuywa, napongela khumbivi ncha vanu, akhavombile evo husihu yemo khuvoni, ulyakhehuminche yuywa.  
\v 28 Khululagelo luhovachagola avanu avasaviwesya uvotehenchi uvovaha, ulyahova elimenyu lyaheapa, lehinehile badala ya lulagelo, akhachagwile umwana, uyahavombikhe ukhuva imwaminifu isihu nchoni.   
\c 8
\cl Sura ya 8 
\p
\v 1 Lino ilitwincha lyu ili tulinave untekhenchi umbaha uvya tamile pasi mkhivoko ikyando mkhigoda ikyavutwa khukhanya.  
\v 2 Umwene vi mbombi pavuva lanche, elihema lya lweli ilyu ili untwa alivikhile, sa khila munu vakhufa.  
\v 3 Ulwakhuva khila ukhuhani umbaho ivikhiwa nu khokhela ni sadako, pwu lunonu ukhuva ni khinu kya kuhumya.  
\v 4 Lino uKlisite ale pakyanya pakilunga, umwene sangale iva kuhani ulwa kuwa vakhidikhile vala avakhahuminche ifirhungilwa ukhukongana ni ndagilo.  
\v 5 Valikhumba ikhinu ikyukyale masigalilo ne khipepe n'chela kya finu fya kukhanya, ahwanine nu Mose upwu avongiwe nu Nguluve upwu anogwa gwa ukhunjenga elihema. “Lola,” UNguluve akhata, “Vomba khila khinu ukhukongana nu mfivelile umwo akhu vonisye pakhyanya pakyamba”.  
\v 6 Pwu lino uKlisite upelile imbombo inonu fincho ulwa khuva navope insayani va lwidihano elinonu, ilyu lelinywile ndwidihano ulunonu.  
\v 7 Pwu lino ingave ulwidihano ulwa kuvutengulilo pwu ulwidihano ulwa kwanja lungale lule ukhuyaga, apo satwa twive ni mbombo ya kulande ulwidihano ulwa vili.  
\v 8 Ulwa khuva uNguluve avile alumanyile ukhuyaga kwa vanu akhata, “Lola, imisikhi igikwincho, 'inchova uNguluve, 'Ita unsikhi ipya nevombile ulwidiheno uluoya paninie ni nyumba ya Isilaeli, ni nyumba ya Yuda.  
\v 9 Salukhale ndu lwidihano ulunivombile paninie nu dada vinyo ikhigono ikyu navatolile kyu mavokho ukhuvalongoncha ukhuhuma khukhilunga ya kuMisri. Ulwakhuva savaliku gendelela mundwidihano lwango, nayune sanilikusagila,' inchova untwa.  
\v 10 Ulwa khuva ulu lwulidihano nivomba kyu nyumba ya Israeli khu figono fya kuvulongolo,' inchova untwa. 'nivekha indagilo nchango mmasage gavene khange nikwandika munumbula ncha vene. Niva Nguluve va vene navope viva vanu vango.  
\v 11 Savakha manyisana umunu nu jirani na khila munu nu lukololwe uvi ita mmanye, “Unkulu deva,” Pwu voni vikumanya une, ukhuhuma udebe mpakha umbaha vavo.  
\v 12 Pyuni kuvavonesya ikhisa kya mbombo ncha vene nchincho sancheyelweli, sanila kumbukha inongwa ncha vene.”  
\v 13 Pwu ukhuta “Kipya,” atengenisye ulwidihano ulwa kwanja ukuva lukulu kulu. Na ilyo ikhulitangasya ukuva likuhuhe khulu lugulila ukhuhega.   
\c 9
\cl Sura ya 9 
\p
\v 1 Leno ulwedikhano ulwa vwutanchi lyale na pono pa khusayela pahelunga nu lwiho lwa nyesayo.  
\v 2 Mu ndyeve mwale neheyumba ekyahunji, patambuliwagwa pavalanche. Apa pupale ne khevelelo khya nyale, mesa ne mikate egya hwelolela.  
\v 3 Hunsana hu mwenda u gwa vele ne ekheyumba ekhenge, patambuliwagwa pavwuvalanche fiicho mwale ne ekhetehelelo ekhyakutehelela.  
\v 4 Mwale ne livohosi lya ndagano elyajengiwe nu talama lwene. Mgati mwale ne beseni lya lutalama elenya manna, ulusaga lwa Haruni ulumelile elinyasi, ni mbavo nzila incha mawe aga lwedehano.  
\v 5 Pakyanya pa livohosi lya lwedehano pale ni fihwani vya wasung'wa avavalanche avagubehile amapapatelo gavene huvulongolo huhegoda kya husayanila, hekhyo twilemwa ukhupanga vononu.  
\v 6 Vwo vamalile ukhutesania ifinu ifi, avatekhenchi valekhwingela ekheyumba ekya khonji ekhyalieve mu hutekhela.  
\v 7 Untekhenchi umbakha alekhwingile mu kheyumba ekhya vele mwene khamo mwakha, salekhumihincha enekhelo ya mwene, kho mbivi incha vanu nchincho vavambile khetasaga.  
\v 8 Umepo umbalanche inchova ukhuta, enjela eya pavuvalanche sayede nduliwe ulwa khova elyeve elya khutengulila lenchige lyemile.  
\v 9 Ekhe khehwani khya sekhe ugwa leno. Fyoni ifivonole ne sadakha ifihomenchiwe leno safiwesya ukhumala amasage ga unyakhutehela.  
\v 10 Ifyakhulya nu uvwubaga fyene vafilonganche ne nekhelo eya khwesukha. Fyoni ifi fyale nu uvulongonchi uwa mbili fifyo vafitesanche pwu ululagelo ulupya uluyaheva luvekhiwa aponu palwene.  
\v 11 UKlisite ainchile ndu ntekhenchi umbaha uva imbombo inonu nchincho inhonchile. Uhugendela uvwuvaha nu kwilanila ne lyeve lelyo salyajengiwe na mavokho ga vanu, vavo sava khelunga ekhe ekhepeliwe.  
\v 12 Yale siyo khunkhisa gwa mene ne ngwada, yale khunkisa gwa mwene uhuta u Klisite aingelaga pavuvalanche khamu nu lotelela khela yumo yumo nu ukhutupelela uwvupokhi wetu uwa majuva goni.  
\v 13 Enave khu nkhisa gwa mene na amapongo nu ukhulagakhencha elyela elya ngwada khu avo avavalanche avakhaliwe khwa Nguluve nukhugevekha emivile gyavene geveminonu,  
\v 14 Uvwu loteleli wa nkhisa gwa Klisite ukhugendela umepo va sikhu nchoni aekhominche yuywa khesita nkole khwa Nguluve, ukhusukhiwa imbivi nchetu ukhuma imbombo imbivi ukhumbombela u Nguluve umwumi?  
\v 15 Ulwa khuva, Klisite insukhiwa va ndagano imya. Ukhumana nele uvufwe vuvalekhile nu vudekhedekhe woni vava va ndagano incha vutanchi, ukhuma mu nongwa nchavene, pwu vwoni avelangiwe nu Nguluve vambelele uvukhale wa vene uwa siku nchoni.  
\v 16 Inave khuile endagano inchitama, levonekhe mu mbufwe uwa munu ola uvealevombile.  
\v 17 Ulwa khuva endagano yiiva na makha upwuvuhumila uvufwe, gasikholi amakha unsekhe unyakhole vomba wipitama.  
\v 18 Vwulevule endagano eya khatale yavekhiwe khenchila nkhisa.  
\v 19 U Mose avile akhominche ululagelo khu vanu voni, atolile ukhisa gwa senga nu gwa mene, paninie na magasi, umwenda undukhu, ne sabuni, nu ukhuminchulila elivangeli na avanu voni.  
\v 20 Pwu akhanchova, “Ugu gwu nkhisa gwa ndagano gugwa avapile u Nguluve ululagilo.”  
\v 21 Vwulevule, akhaminchulila ukhisa pakhianya pa lieve ni ifivombelo ifyavombile khu nekhelo.  
\v 22 Ukhukongana nu lulagilo, khela khenu khisukhiwa nu nkhisa. Khetaduda ukhisa lusikhuli ulusyekhelo.  
\v 23 Pwu yelekhuva ifivchwani vya yinu ifya khukyanya yelekhuva fisukhiwe ne nekhelo eya fidemo. Pwu, ifinu ifya khu kyanya filikhusukhiwa nu nkhisa unonu.  
\v 24 Ulwa khuva Klisite sakhingele pavuvalanche apanchengiwe na mavokho, yeyo khehwani khya khenu. Pwu akhingela khukyanya yoywa, upwalepo leno alepamikho ga Nguluve khu nongwa ncheto.  
\v 25 Saingele ukhu ukhwekhomja enekhelo emisekhe gyoni, ndu umwivombela untekhenchi umbakha, uveaikhwingela pa vuvalanche khela mwakha paninie nu nkhisa gwa yonge,  
\v 26 enave yale ya lweli, pwu ya yiva agatanchiwage khu khingi ukhuma khu vutengulilo wa khelunga. Unsekhe ugu yivombikha khamo na khuvumalelo uwa miakha egyaevonisye nu ukhuhencha uvutulanongwa khu nekhelo ya mwene.  
\v 27 Enave khila munu ukhufwa mara khamo, vwukonga uvukhegi,  
\v 28 ulwa khuva u Klisite aekhominehe mara khamo ukhusukha umbivi incha vingi, aivonekha ulwavele, ukhusita nchivombela imbivi, ulwakhuva khuvupokhi khuvavo vakhulelaga khuluhuvile.   
\c 10
\cl Sura ya 10 
\p
\v 1 Vule vule ululagilo, mwenchenchi gwa imbombo inonu inchikwincha, sionchonchene. Ululagilo lunave salukwidekhana navowo valipipi nu Nguluve kunjila ya Neghelo nchinchila enchuvahumigya avatekhenche imiaka khoni.  
\v 2 Ndalino savilekhile ukhutekela? Ekhegelelo ekheyo khya vanya lwusayo, vagave vasukhiwe khamo, vavilemwa ukhunchi manya imbivi.  
\v 3 Pwu munekhelo incho ekhwani ekya mbivi incha vambighe imiaka gyioni.  
\v 4 Ulwakuva yitakhana khukhisa gwa magida na mapongo ukhunche imbivi.  
\v 5 U Klisite avile inchile pakhilunga anchovile akhata samwanogwe enekhelo, Pwu mwanonchinche umbili.  
\v 6 Samweli khenu munekhelo iyakhu nyanya khumbivi.  
\v 7 Apa nanchovile, “Lola, nivomba ulugano lwakho, Nguluve, nduvuwuyesimblwe, mundivangili.”  
\v 8 Anchovile ndavuwa yenchoviwe pakhya apo: “Samwanogwe enekhelo efya kunyanya khumbivi, samwahovokhe mnumbula ncheyo” Enekhelo enchovite khela ukhokongana nidogilo.  
\v 9 Anchovile, “Lola, pwanile apa ukhuvomba ulugano lwakho”. Avikhile kulu khanchi inyikho incha khatali iliukhunchikhagancha nchila incha vili.  
\v 10 Munyikho incha vili, tutegiwe nu Nguluve nulugano lwa mwene ukhugendela ukhumya khumbili gwa Yesu Klisite khamo khumisiki gyioni.  
\v 11 Lweli khela ntekhenchi inkhwima kutekela insiku nchoni, ikhumya enekhelo yilayila, nchavencha yayilemwa ukhunchikhencha imbivi.  
\v 12 Ulwakhuva uKlisite atekhele khamo khumbivi amanchova goni atamile khukivoko inkyadyo.  
\v 13 Apulikhila avalugu va mwene vakhiwa pasi nu khuva khigoda kya kuvikhila amalunde ga mwene.  
\v 14 Ulukhuva khunjila ya nekhelo nyimo avakaginche isikhu nchoni eivategiwe nu Nguluve.  
\v 15 Nu mepo umepo umbalanche inchova khulifwe. Ulwakuva pavutengulelo anchovile,  
\v 16 “Ulwu lwu lwidihano uluyakheva nivomba paninie na vene vwukhalutile amanchova; inchova u Nguluve: Nivekha ululagilo mgati mu numbula nchavo, nanisimba mu nyala nchavo.”  
\v 17 Pwu akhachova, “Savalanchikhumbukha imbivi ni mbombo nchavo inchifwile”.  
\v 18 Leno bhaho pulule ulusyekhelo khu ava, yesikhuli enekhelo yeyone khu mbivi.  
\v 19 Ulwa khuva, valokolo, tulenuvunchimu ukhwingela pavuvalanche khu nkhisa gwa Yesu.  
\v 20 Eyo njela eyeayedendwile khu mbivi nchetu khu mbile gwa mwene, emia ne nyumi eyigendela mu mwenda.  
\v 21 Ulwakhuva tulenave untekhenchi umbakha mu nyumba ya Nguluve,  
\v 22 Pwu tukhegelelage ne numbula ya welweli khuvumalilo wa lwidikho tuvinchage ne numbula inchilagahe nchiwe inonu ukhuhuma khu vovivi wa masage nu lwa khuva emivele gyetu gesukhiwe na magasi amanonu.  
\v 23 Pwu tubatelele khu makha ulokhuto lwa vonehimu wa lwedekho lwetu, khetasyetukha, ulwa khuva u Nguluve anchovile va yelweli.  
\v 24 Pwu tusagage ukhonkhangancha khela munu ukhunogwa ukhuvomba inonu.  
\v 25 Tusite ukhwelekhelwa ukhulundamana paninie, nduvuvyavigakha avange tutunganage mu numbula, nduvu mwilola isikhu nchihegelile.  
\v 26 Tungave tuvomba amatingo nu ukhupivomba imbivi vwutwembile isyole ya vuyelweli, Enekhelo eyenge eya mbivi sayisigala khange.  
\v 27 Pwu, mbalongolo tupolekhela uvukhegi uwa khudwancha, nu ululimbo lwa mwoto lulanyanya avatula nongwa khwa Nguluve.  
\v 28 Uve avenchaga uveabelile ululagilo lwa Mose ifwa bila khesa mbolongolo mwa watangili vavele ama vadatu.  
\v 29 Ekhegelelo khikhi ekhelutilile ekya livungu vusaga ikhinogelanile khwa umoumo uveabedile umwana va Nguluve, uveavenchaga uveagokhinile unkisa gwa lwedehano ndekhenu ekhesakhevalanche, unkhisa gugwa agwemikhe khwa Nguluve - uveavenchaga uveadukhile umepo va luhungu?  
\v 30 Ulwa khuva tulumanyile yumo uveanchovile, “Uvukhegivwango, nikhomba.” “Unguluve alavakhega avanu vya mwene”.  
\v 31 Khenu kya khudwancha umunu ukhugwila mu mavoko ga Nguluve umuomi!  
\v 32 Khambokha isikhu inchilotile vulwinchile ulumuli, mwagakhile ndeti ukhusipa uluvavo uluvakha.  
\v 33 Mwavekhiwe pavuvalafu nu hubediwa nuhudukhiwa nu hugatanchiwa, mwale paninie na vavo vagendile uvugatale nduvwa.  
\v 34 Ulwa khuva mwale ne numbula ya khesa khuvala avakhongiwe, pwu mwapokhile ulukhekhelo uvukhuvilwa wa vwukhale wenyo, mu khalumanya ukhuta yumwe mwale nu uvukhale uvunonu uwa sikhu nchoni.  
\v 35 Msite ukhuvulekha uvunchimu wenyo, uvunyawokhela vuvakha.  
\v 36 Ulwa khuwa yinogiwa ukhweyu melencha, pwu mwambelele ekhe u Nguluve avavekhile, vomvombile imbombo ncha mwene.  
\v 37 Akhavalilo akhasupi pwu yumo ikhwincha lweli sakhalindidele.  
\v 38 Ugolofu itamaga nulwidikho. Akhave owuya khusana sangakhovokhele.”  
\v 39 Ufwe satulindavene avikhilivukha khusana, ukhuyaga. Ufwe tulivadebe twivanyalwidekho ukhunchilo lela inumbula ncheto.   
\c 11
\cl Sura ya 11 
\p
\v 1 Leno ulwedekho ulwalweli ulwa munu usekhe uguvugu lena ekhenu jasiri. Pu ulwedekho ulwa khenu ekhelebado sakhevonikhe.  
\v 2 Khululagelo ulu avakukhu veto vakhagulile khulwedekho lwavo.  
\v 3 Khulwedekho tulumanyile ukhuta nkherunga khwava Nguluve, inave sakhekhajengiwe ukhukhumana ni finu fifyo filihova fivonekha.  
\v 4 Yale ukhuva inave ulwedekho hoita uHabili akhang'umekhije uNguluve enekhelo enonu khulikho eyakhakhu minche u Kaini. Yale ulwakhuva khundagelo inchii ayiniwe ulwa khuva ale munu wa lwedekho. Nguluve amwedekhe ulwakhuva ya vinu ifwakhakhuminche. Inave evo, Habili bado inchoova, mave afwile.  
\v 5 Yale ukhuta khulwedekho ulwa Enoko atoliwe khukwanya sakhavovone uvufwe. “Sakhavonekhe, ulwakhuva yanchoovivwe pa kwanya pa mwene ukhuta akha nogelanile khwa Nguluve kabla ya khutoliwa khukwyanya.  
\v 6 Apalejila lwedekho sapivombekha ukhuginia uNguluve, ulwakhuva uyie khwinchaa khwa Nguluve yinogiwa edekhe ukhuta uNguluve itama nukhuvapa nukhuvakhelekhila ulupatano ulwavala avavikhundonda.  
\v 7 Yale ukhuva lwedekho khwa Nuhu, inave avungiwe nu Nguluve ukhugendela mumbombo nchiinchoo sajikhale nchakhuvonekhaa, mave elisima elwa Nguluve ancheengile e ngalava khu mbombo ya khuvokhola avamunyumba ya mwene. Khwa khuvomba eva, akhekhegile ekhelunga akhavile nuvukhale uvwayelweli uvuvukhwincha ukhugandela mundwedekho.  
\v 8 Yale ukhuta lwedekho lwa Ibrahimu, avile elangiwe akhedikha nukhuluta esehemu eyiyinogwa ukhupokhela uvuhale. Aha uhegile bila khulumanya ndakhu uhwiluta.  
\v 9 Yale ukhuta ulwedekho atamile nkelunga nurupulekhelo kama igeni. Atamile munyumba pupanie nu Isaka nu Yakobo, avahare avange nu lulagelo lulalula.  
\v 10 Ulwakhuva aletayali ukhupewa esekhemu eyiyelaguliwe nu mbombi va yene aiva ve Nguluve.  
\v 11 Ulwakhuva lwale lwedekho lwa Ibrahimu, nu Sara mwene, vapokhile amakha agakhuvekha ulwanda ulwakhuva vale vagogoro sana, ulwakhuva vambwene uNguluve u khuta imwedesi, uyavavulile ukhuta ikhuvapa umwana udemi.  
\v 12 Ulwakhuva ukhukhuma khwa munu yumo uyarekaribu nu khufwa vakhoriwe avana avasavivalekha. Vale vingi wita nondwe incha khukwanya na vingi wita mbeyu incha manga mulukhanchi ndugasi uluvakha.  
\v 13 Avavoni vafwile khupokhela ulwedekho ulwa lutanchi. Inave evo, vangave vanchiwene nukhunchisogelenchaa khuvutali, vanchoovile ukhuta vale vageni na vagenda njila pakwanya pakherunga.  
\v 14 Khuvala avavinchoova embombo inchii vikhevekhela ukhuta valalondaga ekherunga khwavene.  
\v 15 Ulwakhuva, inave vakhale vikumbukha ekherunga ekhevakha humile, vaviva nusekhe ugwa huvuya.  
\v 16 Ulwakhuva vuyilevo, vinogwaekhe runga ekhenonu, inave khya khukyanya. ulwakhu uNguluve sivona soni ukhwelangiwa Nguluve vavene, ulwakhuva andalile umji khwa ajili yatoo.  
\v 17 Yale ukhuta lwedekho khw Ibarahimu pala upwageriwe, akhang'uninchee u Isaka. Lweli, umwene uyahupelile vunonu ulukhekhelo lwango, ahang'u mwa umwana va mwene yuywa,  
\v 18 Uve pakhwanya pamwene pa nchoovivwe, “Ukhukhuma khwa Isaka uvukhohoa wakho vuva.”  
\v 19 Ibrahimu alumanyile ukhuta uNguluve ale nuvuweso uwakhundonda u Isaka ukhukhuma khuvufwe, nu khunchoova khunchoovelo eya maumbo, ampokhile.  
\v 20 Ulwa khuva lwale lwedekho ukhuta Isaka amwopelile u Yakobo nu Esau ulwakhuva ya mbombo nchooni mchinchikhwi nchaa.  
\v 21 Lwale lwedekho ukhuta uYakobo walepakhuva pa khegono ekhwakhufwa, avapile khela mwana va Yusufu. Yakobo akhabudu, akhegime pakwanya parubekhi lwango.  
\v 22 Yale ukhuva lwedekho lwa Yusufu unsekhe ugwamene vugufikhe ugwa mwisyo, anchoovile uhukhuma khwa vana ava mwene khu Israeli Misri avavulile ukhutola amachege agavene pupaninie.  
\v 23 Lwale lwedekho ukhuta uMusa, vwa holiwe, anikhiwe na valongonchi va mwana edebe uyale inonu, savakhadwade ululagero ulwatwa.  
\v 24 Yale ukhuta lwedekho uMusa, upwavile munu embakha, aberile ukhwelangiwa mwana va binti Farao.  
\v 25 Pakhuva umwene, achaguliwa ukhuchangila etabu paninie na vanu ava Nguluve pa khuva savakhakhovove ilaha nimbivi inchaa sekhe.  
\v 26 Avekhile soni ukhukonga uKlisite ukhuta vuvutayali vuvakha ukhwevekhela Misri ulwa khuva akhakasinchee amikho agamwene ulwakhuva vupewa usekhe ugugukhwinchaa.  
\v 27 Yale ukhuva lwedekhe ukhuta umusu akhumile khu Misri. Sahadwade uvukalale vwatwa, alwakhuva aiyu melinche ukhulola ukhusakhuvonekha.  
\v 28 Yale ukhuva lwedekhe ukhuta aibite ekhwakha nu khududelela unkisa, khukhuta unangi uva nglorwa va khwa nchaa alemwe ukhuvibata avakholwa va hwancha ava demiva khu waisrael.  
\v 29 Yale ukhuva lwedekhe ukhuta vage ndile munyanja eya shamu ndolwakherunga ekhekafu. Usekhe ugwa wamisri uluvakhagelile ukhugenda, valeviwe.  
\v 30 Yale ukhuva khulwedekho ulwa ruvego ulwa Yeriko lukha gwile pasi, puvakha rwugile isikhu saba.  
\v 31 Yale ukhuva khulwedekho ulwa Rahabu ukahaba ula sakhagwe paninie na vala avasavale vagorofu, ulwakhuva avapokhile avavonchii nu khuva vekha pavunonu.  
\v 32 Na nenchoove ndakhekhe? Ulwakhuva usekhe sagwihwela ukhupanga aga Gideoni, Barak, Samsoni, Yeftha, Daudi, Samwel ni nchaa vanya malago,  
\v 33 Avagendile ulwedekho vakhawe sinchee uvulongonchi, vavombile elweli, na vakhupelile indagano. Vabenchiinchee emilomo egwa ngarama.  
\v 34 Vahanchiminchee ingufu incha mwoto, vakhapagile ulwugi lwa mundu, vakhaponile ukhukhuma mbutamu, vale vakangale humbancha, vakhanchangile ava mugambo avageni ukhunyila.  
\v 35 Avadala vakhapokhile avafwe vavene khulugendo ulwa khunchu ukha. Avange vale nuvu khuvelwa, khesita khwedeha ukhunehilekha inyavukhe lenu khukhuta vapate uvunchoovele vwa khunchukha tena.  
\v 36 Avange vikhangayikha khwasi hakha ne vibokho, mweene, atanu khukungwa nukhwingenchiwa igati mbukungwa.  
\v 37 Vatoviwe na mawe. Vagediwe nulukegetelo fipiligapiliga. Vabudiwe khumundu, vakharutile nii ngwembe incha nglosi nii ngwembe inchaa mene vale vatangilwa, vaendelile ukhulemala tena vavombiwe amavivi  
\v 38 (gago ikherunga sakhikhano gelanile ukhuva nago), vuvi khangayikha ndunyikha, mufiwamba, igati mumanga na mugati maguli aga pavodongo.  
\v 39 Inave avanu voni vakhedekhiwe nu Nguluve ulwa huva vale nulwedeko lwavo, savahapokhele ekhya valagile.  
\v 40 UNguluve alongwile khukhotupa ekhenu ekhegorofu, inave evo ufwe savakhale viwesya ukhulekhania.   
\c 12
\cl Sura ya 12 
\p
\v 1 Pakhwa tuchunguti liwe nilivengo elivaha lya vasaidi lulage khila khinu eikhituhili khila khui mbivi n'chi, n'chin'chii khutu chungutila khimbivi. tunyilage uluvilo khunjila ya masindano agali khuvulongolo khulufye.  
\v 2 Tulolage amiho getu khwa Yesu, uvi atalile nukhu mali hecha uluidikho letu, uvi khunjila ya lugano iya vikhiwe khuvolongolo khu mwene aeidikhe ekhidamin'gani akha beda isoni, pasi pa khivokho ekyandune na pakhigoda kya Nguluve.  
\v 3 Puyinoguoa ukhusagila ula uvia esikhe amamenyu ga vikalale ukhuma khuva tula nongwa, pa mbombo ya mwene pange tusite ukhugatala ukhuchimila inumbula n'chelo.  
\v 4 Samvu tabikhe nukhutesekha ukhusindana nvvutula nongwa mpakha ukhu sila ugisa.  
\v 5 Apange msamilwe ukhu gingn'chiwa ukhu khuvalanga kama vana avagosi: “Manango usite ukhu gatolela khi webepe amamenyu ga Daada nange usite ukhu kalala viikhukhu vula umwene.  
\v 6 Hange daada ikhu gana vivoni uvia ganile, itova khu mwana uvisikhu mpokela.  
\v 7 Umelila etabu ndukhuganiwa nu Nguluve. Uvi uhanga yikha nu mwene, nduvuihanga yikha na vana, mwana veni uvi udadaye si ulesya ukhugana?  
\v 8 Eingave khusikhuli ukhudigiwa ukhu twi voni tuli paninwe, puyiva umwe muliva vivi hange samli vana va mwene.  
\v 9 Paninwe na ga tukhale nava baba ava khimbili nukhu vungiwa pani nwe nago, tulikhuva choada. Ye satunoguoa ukhuvadwada ava Baba va kheiroho tutamage?  
\v 10 Pakhuva ava baba veto valikhutu vunga ei miakha midebe nduvu yevomkhe sawa khuvene, pakhuva uuNguluve ikhitukemela nei faida yeto tuhange uvuvalan'che wa mwene.  
\v 11 Yesikhuli eingomo ei yeyihovosya khusikhi ugwa. Gwiva nuluvavo paninwe nilyo, yehola isekhe n'cha lunon'chehencho lwa vuvalan'che ava fundisiwe nalo.  
\v 12 Haya lenu eimikha amavokho agalegehile nukhu fugama na malunde genyo amabofu gakave amagha khavili;  
\v 13 Golosya einjila n'cha nyayo n'chinyo umvnu uviaven'chaga unde male, alongon'chiwe khuvuyagi pa khuva yinogiwa ukhupona.  
\v 14 Londaga ulu noon'che hencho na vanu voni na vavala n'che pakhuwa bila huo asipali avyakhwa ukhumbona uNguluve.  
\v 15 Mve miho asite ukhuvapo na yumo uvakhwva patali ne khisa kya Nguluve, nukhu humila undela gwa lioyo ugugwimela nu khugega ei tabu nu khugweisya vingi.  
\v 16 Mulolage pakhuva yesipali ei nongwa au umunu uve sagolome ndwu Esau, uviagun'chinche uvaholiwa kwa luta n'chi akhakosya ei hakhi.  
\v 17 Nayumwe mulumanyile ukhuta avele inogwa ulusayo akhabeliwa pakhuwa saa pele paninwue nu baba va mwene, paninuue nukhulonda sana ninyi hon'chi.  
\v 18 Pakhuwa samwa n'che pakyamba ei khikhiwesya ukhugusuwa, ei kyamba eikhikhi khawakha umwoto ei hisi, ei yikatesya eitamaa ne tabu.  
\v 19 Sanwa in'che ne savuti n'cha tarumbeta na mamenyu ne savuti n'chi sababesya avipolikha vasite ukhu dova ei limenyu lyolyoni khuvene.  
\v 20 Pakhwa sava khavuesye ukhuikasya pakfula ei khilamuliwa, yekha va hata ifikanu ifigusya eikyamba fito viwe na mawe.  
\v 21 N'cha khudwa n'cha sana n'cha lolile uu Musa akha chova, nedwadile sana nukhutetema.”  
\v 22 Badala ya yene mwin'chele khukhamba kya Sayuni ne khulunga kya Nguluve aliye hai, ei Yelusalem ya khukyanya, na vasun'gwa elfu khin'chigo, avihekhela.  
\v 23 Mwin'chile paluhenda mano lwa vaholiwa va khwanja ava va simbiue khukyanya khwa Nguluve undamu n'chi va voni ni numbula n'cha vavalan'che avavidikhiwe.  
\v 24 Mwin'chile khwa Yesu upatanisi va ligano ei lipya khu kisa uguguchedeliue gwiichova ei nonu khulekho ukisa gwa Habili.  
\v 25 Ulolage usite ukhube la yumo uvi inchova ukhuta eingave savakhepukhe upu vakha mbelile yumo uvi akha vakemeli mukhilunga, pakhuva satuwesya ukhulepa ei ngave, tugevakha patanli, khwa ula uvi atu vulele ukhuma khukyanya.  
\v 26 Khusikhi ugwa ei savuti ya mwene yelikhisinche eikhilunga. Hata leno yevikhile eili Agano nukhuchova badu khavile tena yitikhisya ikhilunga na khukhu kyanya.  
\v 27 Amamenyu afa, “Mara khamo tena,” yivonesya ukhuhega khwa vinu, ifitetemesya ifi vinu vila ifi vumbiale, pkfuwa ifi me ni sfitetema fisigale.  
\v 28 Po yinofiwa tupokhele uludeva ulusatu tetemesiwa, tuhovokhe tuhovokhe mu hali yakhu ginwa uNguluve nukhuidikha paninwe nukhunyenyekhela katika kicho.  
\v 29 Pakhuva uNguluve vito mwoto ugwilya.   
\c 13
\cl Sura ya 13 
\p
\v 1 Basi ulugano lwa lukalo luleendelee.  
\v 2 Musite ukhusamwa ukhuva karibisya avageni manya pakhi vomba ewo, vingi vavakalibisye avasungwa bila kulumanya.  
\v 3 Khumbukha voni avali mli khifungo avange mkhale navo, nage mivili gwenyo gwa vombeliwe nda vene.  
\v 4 Nidova uvutegulane vudwadiwage na vanu voni nei eikhihaga khwa vutegulane kheve safi, pakhuva uNguluve ukhuvahiga voni avaligu na vamalaya.  
\v 5 Injila n'chinyo n'cha vutamo n'chive nomu mundu gano lwa hela mve vanu vakhulisekha neifinu ifi mule na fyo. Pakhuva uNguluve vioyu achovile, “Sanikhuvalegha umwe nukhuva yan'cha.”  
\v 6 Basi mulisekhe pu tun'chovage na makha u Daada vintangeli vango sanidwadaga. Umunu ei khungaha khekhi?”  
\v 7 Muvasayilagevala avakhavalongo n'chaga avakhan'chovaga elimenyu lya Nguluve khuluemwe, hange mkumbukhage ulugendo ne migendelo gwa vene, ei gila einyedikho n'cha vene.  
\v 8 UYesu Klisiti vi ula pamihe nei lelo, ni sikhu nchooni.  
\v 9 Usite ukhulongonchiwa nu lumanyisyo amageni lunonu inumbula n'chinchengiwe mkhisa sio ndulagilo lwa kya kyulura, ago sagiokhu vatanga avitama mwago.  
\v 10 Tulinakyo eikhite khelo kya vala ava vivomba mugati mutembile vi n'chila luhusa ulwa khulya.  
\v 11 Khunjila ya mikisa gwa fikanu n'chi humen'chiwe nekhelo khunjila yavo tulanongwa, yaletiwe nutekhaen'chi mugati muvavalan'che, neimiviili gya chene gwanyanywe panjika palikambi.  
\v 12 Nayu Yesu atesikhe panji pavo jenge ili yevenekhelo khuvanu ukhugendela mukisa gwa mwene.  
\v 13 Pu uno tulutage panji pavu n'chenge, tukhagege ulubeelo lwa mwene.  
\v 14 Pakhuva tuvan'chila vutamo uwa sikhu inyingi pakhilunga eihe. Khunjila eiye tulonde uvun'chenge uvuvukhwin'cha.  
\v 15 Ukhugendela khwa Yesu yinofiwa khila misekhi ukhwihomwa nekelo khwa Nguluve, tuginieage tukave isekhen'cha milomo gyeto, n'cheidekhe eilitawa lya mwene.  
\v 16 Usite ukhusanwa ukhuvomba amanonu, nukhutanga yumwe khwa yumwe. Pakhuva einekhelo ndeiyo uNguluve inogwa fin'cho.  
\v 17 Mwidekhage nu khwikha pasi pavalongon'chi venyo, pakhuva vigendelela ukhudema inumbula n'chenyo, ndavanu avavihumya eimbalilo n'chenyo. Eidekha pu avalongon'chi venyo vavalongon'cha nulu hekhelo, sio nuluvipo ulusalu khi vatanga.  
\v 18 Tweisayage pakhuva tulumanyile ukhuta tulinamasage amanonu, twinogwa uvutamo uvunonu neili sima pa mbombo n'choni.  
\v 19 Gooni nikhuvapa amaga muvombe n'chi ili muvuye khumonyo khimbeve.  
\v 20 Leno uNguluve valugano uvei avagegile ukhuma khuvufye undongon'chi umbaha va ng'osi, Bwana veito Yesu, Klisite khunjila ya ndagano ya sikhun'choni,  
\v 21 Ukhuvapa amakha gakhila mbombo ei nonu, nukhukonga indagilo n'cha mwene, nukhuvomba eimbombo ei nonu igati ndyufye, eiye nogile pamiho ga mwene, ukhugendela khwa Yesu Klisite, khu mwene vuve vuvalanche wa sikhun'choni. Amina.  
\v 22 Lino nikhukhupa amakha lukolo lwango, ukhukongana nei limenyu lya khukhupa amakha lilyo nesi mbile lesopi khuliumwe.  
\v 23 Mulumanye ukhuta ulukolo lwenyu u Timoti vandekhile mumbwa vukhe paninie numwene ni khwi n'cha khukhuva vona usikhe gunga fikhe.  
\v 24 Ponwa avalongon'chi vakho voninava kelesite voni. Vala avavihuma khuu itali vikhuva ponwa.  
\v 25 Uluhekhelo luve numwene mwe voni.   